Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">Os pre&ccedil;os de venda ao p&uacute;blico, seja para um cliente individual ou uma companhia, incluem onde aplic&aacute;vel o Imposto sobre o Valor Acrescentado (IVA).</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 11.25pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 11.25pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 10pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-outline-level: 5;\"><a name=\"ponto12\"></a><strong><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 9pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">12. CONDI&Ccedil;&Otilde;ES DE DEVOLU&Ccedil;&Atilde;O</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 11.25pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt;\">Regra Geral para devolu&ccedil;&atilde;o</span></strong><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\"><br /> Se o utilizador pretender devolver um produto dever&aacute; faz&