: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">O Contrato entre o Vendedor e o utilizador vincula as partes e os respectivos sucessores e cession&aacute;rios.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 11.25pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">O utilizador n&atilde;o poder&aacute; transferir, ceder ou onerar a sua posi&ccedil;&atilde;o contratual, ou por qualquer outro meio dispor do Contrato ou de quaisquer direitos ou obriga&ccedil;&otilde;es dele decorrentes, sem o consentimento pr&eacute;vio do Vendedor, dado por escrito.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 11.25pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">O Vendedor pode transferir, ceder ou onerar a sua posi&ccedil;&atilde;o contratual, sub-contratar ou por qualquer outro meio dispor do Contrato ou de quaisquer direitos ou obriga&ccedil;&otilde;es dele decorrentes, em qualquer momento da sua vig&ecirc;ncia. N&atilde;o obstante, nenhuma transfer&ecirc;ncia, cess&atilde;o ou onera&ccedil;&atilde;o de tal posi&ccedil;&atilde;o, ou acto de disposi&ccedil;&atilde;o do contrato, poder&aacute; ter por efeito a limita&ccedil;&atilde;o dos direitos legais do utilizador enquanto consumidor ou reduzir, ou limitar de qualquer modo, qualquer garantia prestada pelo Vendedor ao utilizador de forma expressa ou impl&iacute;cita.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 11.25pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 11.25pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 10pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-outline-level: 5;\"><a name=\"ponto19\"></a><strong><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 9pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">19. EVENTOS FORA DO CONTROLO DO VENDEDOR</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 11.25pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">O Vendedor n&atilde;o ser&aacute; respons&aacute;vel por incumprimento, ou mora no cumprimento, de qualquer obriga&ccedil;&atilde;o decorrente do Contrato que seja devida a evento fora do seu controlo razo&aacute;vel (\"Evento de For&ccedil;a Maior\"). <br /> Um Evento de For&ccedil;a Maior compreende qualquer acontecimento, acto ou omiss&atilde;o, fora do controlo razo&aacute;vel do Vendedor e inclui, em particular (mas n&atilde;o de forma exclusiva), os seguintes:</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: square;\">\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\">\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: small;\"></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: disc; direction: ltr;\">\r\n<li style=\"color: #777777; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;\">\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 200%; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 10pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: l0 level3 lfo6; tab-stops: list 108.0pt;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; line-height: 200%; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">Greves, lock-outs e outras ac&ccedil;&otilde;es laborais</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;\">\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 200%; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 10pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: l0 level3 lfo6; tab-stops: list 108.0pt;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; line-height: 200%; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">Levantamentos civis, tumulto, invas&atilde;o, ataque terrorista ou amea&ccedil;a de ataque terrorista, guerra (declarada ou n&atilde;o) ou amea&ccedil;a de preparativos de guerra.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;\">\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 200%; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 10pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: l0 level3 lfo6; tab-stops: list 108.0pt;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; line-height: 200%; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">Fogo, explos&atilde;o, tempestade, inunda&ccedil;&atilde;o, tremor de terra, afundamento, epidemia ou outro desastre natural.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;\">\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 200%; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 10pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: l0 level3 lfo6; tab-stops: list 108.0pt;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; line-height: 200%; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">Impossibilidade do uso de caminho-de-ferro, de transportes mar&iacute;timos, a&eacute;reos, rodovi&aacute;rios ou outros meios p&uacute;blicos ou privados de transporte.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;\">\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 200%; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 10pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: l0 level3 lfo6; tab-stops: list 108.0pt;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; line-height: 200%; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">Impossibilidade do uso de redes de telecomunica&ccedil;&otilde;es p&uacute;blicas ou privadas.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;\">\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 200%; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 10pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: l0 level3 lfo6; tab-stops: list 108.0pt;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; line-height: 200%; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">Leis, decretos, regulamentos ou restri&ccedil;&otilde;es do Governo.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 200%; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 10pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: l0 level3 lfo6; tab-stops: list 108.0pt;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; line-height: 200%; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">Quaisquer greves, interrup&ccedil;&otilde;es ou acidentes que afectem servi&ccedil;os postais ou de transporte relevantes.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 11.25pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">A obriga&ccedil;&atilde;o de cumprimento do Vendedor em qualquer Contrato ficar&aacute; suspensa pelo tempo que durar um Evento de For&ccedil;a Maior e dar&aacute; lugar a uma prorroga&ccedil;&atilde;o do respectivo prazo equivalente aquela dura&ccedil;&atilde;o. O Vendedor far&aacute; esfor&ccedil;os razo&aacute;veis para p&ocirc;r termo a um Evento de For&ccedil;a Maior, ou para encontrar solu&ccedil;&atilde;o que permita o cumprimento das suas obriga&ccedil;&otilde;es contratuais apesar da exist&ecirc;ncia de um Evento de For&ccedil;a Maior.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 11.25pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 11.25pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 10pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-outline-level: 5;\"><a name=\"ponto20\"></a><strong><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 9pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">20. REN&Uacute;NCIA</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 11.25pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">Se o Vendedor, em qualquer momento da vig&ecirc;ncia do Contrato, se abstiver de exigir o cumprimento estrito de alguma obriga&ccedil;&atilde;o que para o utilizador resulta do Contrato ou dos presentes Termos, ou de exercer qualquer direito ou faculdade neles previstos para p&ocirc;r termo a esse incumprimento, tal n&atilde;o constituir&aacute; ren&uacute;ncia a esses direitos e faculdades e n&atilde;o isentar&aacute; o utilizador do cumprimento das suas obriga&ccedil;&otilde;es.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 11.25pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">A ren&uacute;ncia do Vendedor ao exerc&iacute;cio de algum direito ou faculdade, perante uma determinada situa&ccedil;&atilde;o de incumprimento do utilizador n&atilde;o significa ren&uacute;ncia a direitos ou faculdades face a uma situa&ccedil;&atilde;o de incumprimento posterior.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 11.25pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">A ren&uacute;ncia do Vendedor a qualquer direito resultante do Contrato ou dos presentes Termos apenas ser&aacute; eficaz se constar de comunica&ccedil;&atilde;o escrita enviada ao utilizador pela forma prevista na cl&aacute;usula Comunica&ccedil;&otilde;es, onde aquele declare expressamente que renuncia.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 11.25pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 11.25pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 10pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-outline-level: 5;\"><a name=\"ponto21\"></a><strong><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 9pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">21. REDU&Ccedil;&Atilde;O</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 11.25pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">A declara&ccedil;&atilde;o de invalidade, ilegalidade ou inefic&aacute;cia, por autoridade competente, de qualquer uma das disposi&ccedil;&otilde;es dos presentes Termos &amp; Condi&ccedil;&otilde;es n&atilde;o afectar&aacute; nenhuma das restantes disposi&ccedil;&otilde;es, que continuar&atilde;o em pleno vigor.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 11.25pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 11.25pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 10pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-outline-level: 5;\"><a name=\"ponto22\"></a><strong><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 9pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">22. ACORDO INTEGRAL</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 11.25pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">Os presentes Termos e qualquer documento neles referido constituem o acordo integral estabelecido entre as partes relativamente &agrave; forma&ccedil;&atilde;o de um Contrato e prevalecem sobre qualquer eventual acordo, entendimento ou combina&ccedil;&atilde;o anteriores, sob a forma escrita ou oral.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 11.25pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">Ambas as partes reconhecem que, ao celebrarem o Contrato, nenhuma delas baseou a respectiva motiva&ccedil;&atilde;o em declara&ccedil;&atilde;o, compromisso ou promessa feita pela outra, ou que pudesse considerar-se impl&iacute;cita em algo que tivesse sido dito ou escrito em negocia&ccedil;&otilde;es ocorridas entre as partes em momento anterior &agrave; celebra&ccedil;&atilde;o do Contrato, salvo quando o contr&aacute;rio resulte dos presentes Termos.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 11.25pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">Nenhuma das partes poder&aacute; prevalecer-se do facto de a outra ter produzido afirma&ccedil;&atilde;o n&atilde;o verdadeira, oral ou por escrito, anteriormente &agrave; celebra&ccedil;&atilde;o de um Contrato (salvo quando tal afirma&ccedil;&atilde;o tenha sido feita com fraude) e apenas poder&aacute; socorrer-se das regras do incumprimento contratual que resultam dos presentes Termos.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 11.25pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 11.25pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 10pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-outline-level: 5;\"><a name=\"