#777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 11.25pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 10pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-outline-level: 5;\"><a name=\"ponto22\"></a><strong><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 9pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">22. ACORDO INTEGRAL</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 11.25pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">Os presentes Termos e qualquer documento neles referido constituem o acordo integral estabelecido entre as partes relativamente &agrave; forma&ccedil;&atilde;o de um Contrato e prevalecem sobre qualquer eventual acordo, entendimento ou combina&ccedil;&atilde;o anteriores, sob a forma escrita ou oral.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 11.25pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">Ambas as partes reconhecem que, ao celebrarem o Contrato, nenhuma delas baseou a respectiva motiva&ccedil;&atilde;o em declara&ccedil;&atilde;o, compromisso ou promessa feita pela outra, ou que pudesse considerar-se impl&iacute;cita em algo que tivesse sido dito ou escrito em negocia&ccedil;&otilde;es ocorridas entre as partes em momento anterior &agrave; celebra&ccedil;&atilde;o do Contrato, salvo quando o contr&aacute;rio resulte dos presentes Termos.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 11.25pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">Nenhuma das partes poder&aacute; prevalecer-se do facto de a outra ter produzido afirma&ccedil;&atilde;o n&atilde;o verdadeira, oral ou por escrito, anteriormente &agrave; celebra&ccedil;&atilde;o de um Contrato (salvo quando tal afirma&ccedil;&atilde;o tenha sido feita com fraude) e apenas poder&aacute; socorrer-se das regras do incumprimento contratual que resultam dos presentes Termos.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 11.25pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 11.25pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 10pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-outline-level: 5;\"><a name=\"ponto23\"><strong><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 9pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">23. ALTERA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O DOS TERMOS DE SERVI&Ccedil;O PELO VENDEDOR</span></strong></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 11.25pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-bookmark: ponto23;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">O Vendedor tem o direito de alterar os presentes Termos de Servi&ccedil;o a qualquer altura. O utilizador est&aacute; sujeito aos princ&iacute;pios e termos em vigor &agrave; data da sua encomenda, salvo se a lei ou autoridade competente impuserem qualquer altera&ccedil;&atilde;o aos mesmos (e sendo tais altera&ccedil;&otilde;es aplic&aacute;veis &agrave;s encomendas j&aacute; efectuadas).</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; color: #000000; line-height: 11.25pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-bookmark: ponto23;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 8.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; line-height: 11.25pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-outline-level: 5;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 9pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: PT;\">24. LEI E FORO APLIC&Aacute;VEIS</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: small;\"> </s